  "details": "Python image processing library.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nPillow is a PIL (Python Imaging Library) fork. Affected versions of this package are vulnerable to Improper Input Validation. When the path to the temporary directory on Linux or macOS contained a space, this would break removal of the temporary image file after im.show() (and related actions), and potentially remove an unrelated file.(CVE-2022-24303)",
